":"codeListing","code":["https:\/\/raw.githubusercontent.com\/wipfli\/foursquare-os-places-pmtiles\/refs\/heads\/main\/style.json"]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"The neat thing about this style is that it only uses PMTiles vector sources. PMTiles can be hosted with a relatively simple file server (or file hosting service) instead of a more complex specialized tile server.","type":"text"}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"image","identifier":"pmtiles-demo.png"}]}]}],"seeAlsoSections":[{"identifiers":["doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre-Native-for-iOS\/AnimatedLineExample","doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre-Native-for-iOS\/WebAPIDataExample","doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre-Native-for-iOS\/LineStyleLayerExample","doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre-Native-for-iOS\/DDSCircleLayerExample","doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre-Native-for-iOS\/POIAlongRouteExample","doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre-Native-for-iOS\/GeoJSON"],"generated":true,"anchor":"Styling-and-Dynamic-Data","title":"Styling and Dynamic Data"}],"references":{"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre-Native-for-iOS/WebAPIDataExample":{"kind":"article","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Showing data from an API with custom styling and interaction"}],"type":"topic","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre-native-for-ios\/webapidataexample","title":"Showing data from an API","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre-Native-for-iOS\/WebAPIDataExample","role":"article"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre-Native-for-iOS/LineStyleLayerExample":{"type":"topic","title":"Using GeoJSON with a line style layer","kind":"article","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre-Native-for-iOS\/LineStyleLayerExample","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre-native-for-ios\/linestylelayerexample","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"A